text.section:
As an alternative to the slow-moving vehicle emblem, one (1)-inch-wide white or silver reflective tape may be used on motorless slow-moving vehicles as follows:
The rear of the vehicle shall be covered with a minimum of one hundred (100) square inches of the reflective tape;
The reflective tape on the rear of the vehicle shall, at a minimum, outline the entire rear of the vehicle;
Each side of the vehicle shall be covered with a minimum of thirty-six (36) square inches of reflective tape; and
The highest point of the left front of the vehicle shall be covered with a minimum of twenty-four (24) square inches of reflective tape.
